  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/5b2a6b177f1f7f64f910f475e11d150e.avif?t=1741404108\" width=620 height=70 /></span><br><br><strong>Become your favorite critter, don your fanciest hat, join your friends in a lobby and start blasting them! Experience a collection of different maps to battle on, top the leaderboards, and unleash havoc. Laserstorm is all about chaos, so expect as such!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/3f8a3bf20b639b6095275b194efcac75.poster.avif?t=1741404108\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/3f8a3bf20b639b6095275b194efcac75.webm?t=1741404108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/3f8a3bf20b639b6095275b194efcac75.mp4?t=1741404108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/954d955f520cd71a0c90e4f725d24c62.avif?t=1741404108\" width=620 height=70 /></span><br><br><strong>This experience is meant to be shared with friends! Grab 3 of your pals and have them join the action! However, public lobbies can be made, so if you don't have any friends willing to take the jump with you, that's okay!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/c0f29a1f5dc463ff27cfe5ca581fc51b.poster.avif?t=1741404108\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/c0f29a1f5dc463ff27cfe5ca581fc51b.webm?t=1741404108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/c0f29a1f5dc463ff27cfe5ca581fc51b.mp4?t=1741404108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/7cd6a16730341b2fc4d6d6a7d9d0700a.avif?t=1741404108\" width=620 height=70 /></span><br><br><strong>With a selection of maps to choose from, and more to come in the future, the lasers can never get boring! Calculate those angles and break your friends open like a cold one. With an array of powerups you can grab, the fun will never end, so long as you keep on shooting!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/5e43c696a5c807351b2dc63cda827032.poster.avif?t=1741404108\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/5e43c696a5c807351b2dc63cda827032.webm?t=1741404108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/5e43c696a5c807351b2dc63cda827032.mp4?t=1741404108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/323ba342c9f13096531475b921ff07f3.avif?t=1741404108\" width=620 height=70 /></span><br><br><strong>Our Discord is linked here in the store page, and you can also receive a link from in-game. Feel free to reach out to a developer!</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/5b2a6b177f1f7f64f910f475e11d150e.avif?t=1741404108\" width=620 height=70 /></span><br><br><strong>Become your favorite critter, don your fanciest hat, join your friends in a lobby and start blasting them! Experience a collection of different maps to battle on, top the leaderboards, and unleash havoc. Laserstorm is all about chaos, so expect as such!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/3f8a3bf20b639b6095275b194efcac75.poster.avif?t=1741404108\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/3f8a3bf20b639b6095275b194efcac75.webm?t=1741404108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/3f8a3bf20b639b6095275b194efcac75.mp4?t=1741404108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/954d955f520cd71a0c90e4f725d24c62.avif?t=1741404108\" width=620 height=70 /></span><br><br><strong>This experience is meant to be shared with friends! Grab 3 of your pals and have them join the action! However, public lobbies can be made, so if you don't have any friends willing to take the jump with you, that's okay!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/c0f29a1f5dc463ff27cfe5ca581fc51b.poster.avif?t=1741404108\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860400/extras/c0f29a1f5dc463ff27cfe5c